---
const title = "Our Vision";
const declaration = [
  "We are Dominion City!!!",
  "Dominion City Canary Wharf is a model church dedicated to raising and transforming lives in Canary Wharf and its surrounding environs. We are a thriving community of 5,000 members who are well-grounded priests and kings, rooted in deep spiritual growth and worship. From our 10,000-seat multi-complex in the heart of the city, we equip our members - babies, young and old to excel in their divine callingâ€”balancing a life of the Spirit with a commitment to leadership and societal impact.",
